1
00:00:11,390 --> 00:00:13,210
Our late-night delivery is here.

2
00:00:14,890 --> 00:00:16,310
Sorry.

3
00:00:16,310 --> 00:00:17,770
I'll go grab it.

4
00:00:18,940 --> 00:00:20,770
We'll finish this later.

5
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:22,260
Promise?

6
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:27,080
You promise, right?

7
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:32,450
(It's been so long.
My heart is beating out of my chest.)

8
00:00:32,450 --> 00:00:35,040
(I could never say that out loud.)

9
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,700
Ooh!

10
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:39,410
Omurice! Omu...

11
00:00:39,830 --> 00:00:42,580
Oh my god, this looks amazing!

12
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,330
Hey, want some?

13
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:46,420
No, it's way too late.

14
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:47,760
Aw, come on.

15
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,970
It's going to be delicious.

16
00:00:50,260 --> 00:00:51,630
Just one bite?

17
00:00:51,890 --> 00:00:54,300
I'll feed you.

18
00:00:54,430 --> 00:00:55,510
Well...

19
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:58,390
Okay, just one bite, alright?

20
00:01:03,770 --> 00:01:04,770
Okay.

21
00:01:05,230 --> 00:01:06,780
Here, say ah.

22
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:13,160
Stop smirking and give it to me.

23
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:14,530
Haha, alright.

24
00:01:14,530 --> 00:01:15,490
Here, say ah.

25
00:01:15,490 --> 00:01:16,230
Mmm.

26
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:17,950
Wow, that's delicious!

27
00:01:17,950 --> 00:01:19,620
Right?
See what you would've missed?

28
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:20,500
Yeah.

29
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:22,170
Time to dig in.

30
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:26,420
Mmm! So good!

31
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:29,380
Once I finish this,
I need to get ready for work.

32
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:31,050
Do you have work tomorrow?

33
00:01:31,050 --> 00:01:32,050
Yeah.

34
00:01:32,050 --> 00:01:33,970
I have to leave early in the morning.

35
00:01:33,970 --> 00:01:35,340
Sorry in advance if I wake you.

36
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,720
Take your time, no rush.

37
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,140
I see.

38
00:01:40,310 --> 00:01:43,650
Then we should get to bed early tonight.

39
00:01:46,110 --> 00:01:47,730
What?

40
00:01:52,490 --> 00:01:55,280
Is that your cute way
of asking to sleep together?
